 <h2>Key Points:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>&#8649; Image galleries can vary from simple, trendy, sophisticated, code-heavy, or very technical. You really need to weigh your options toward what your brand (or purpose/aim) is really trying to convey. Use something that complements the style of the entire site as a whole.</li><br>
        <li>&#8649; Keep responsiveness in mind, pick something that is adaptable and responsive to all device sizes.</li><br>
